, "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3706, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 220209, "username": "jzdxeb", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jzdxeb", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/948cccb2ef478d352b58c67338d0bc8d?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/948cccb2ef478d352b58c67338d0bc8d?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/948cccb2ef478d352b58c67338d0bc8d?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1489128867, "last_modified": 1489128867, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "linch97", "last_touched": 1783474553, "title": "银行科技欲离职求打醒", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1225545", "created": 1783400614, "deleted": 0, "content": "社招进银行，这两年科技换天（一把手换人），项目黄了，小领导出走，打杂，混日子中，近期换了个中层小领导、不待见这个人，主观认为人品不行，溜须拍马，使绊子。 欲离职大龄码农 boss 脉脉 基本没个响声儿。怎么破", "content_rendered": "社招进银行，这两年科技换天（一把手换人），项目黄了，小领导出走，打杂，混日子中，近期换了个中层小领导、不待见这个人，主观认为人品不行，溜须拍马，使绊子。 欲离职大龄码农 boss 脉脉 基本没个响声儿。怎么破", "last_modified": 1783400986, "replies": 71, "id": 1225545}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1754172750", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1754172750", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 12890, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1754172750", "stars": 6207, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 777785, "username": "adz2k", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/adz2k", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0097d2b884216cfea9ff0a2c9584716a?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0097d2b884216cfea9ff0a2c9584716a?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0097d2b884216cfea9ff0a2c9584716a?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1765432543, "last_modified": 1765432543, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "JerrySDC", "last_touched": 1783451429, "title": "国行红米手机有推荐吗？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1225464", "created": 1783388729, "deleted": 0, "content": "一直是苹果全家桶用户\r\n\r\n想先入一台国行的主力机去填补苹果机无法覆盖到的功能区间\r\n\r\n身边有朋友推荐红米的手机\r\n\r\n请问现在红米手机入手哪部比较好\r\n\r\n要冲新机吗还是就买二手？", "content_rendered": "<p>一直是苹果全家桶用户</p>\n<p>想先入一台国行的主力机去填补苹果机无法覆盖到的功能区间</p>\n<p>身边有朋友推荐红米的手机</p>\n<p>请问现在红米手机入手哪部比较好</p>\n<p>要冲新机吗还是就买二手？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783388729, "replies": 70, "id": 1225464}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1747623425", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1747623425", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 11195, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1747623425", "stars": 2388, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 598387, "username": "carverReal", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/carverReal", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7ae/d502/598387_mini.png?m=1681798579", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7ae/d502/598387_normal.png?m=1681798579", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7ae/d502/598387_large.png?m=1681798579", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/e7ae/d502/598387_xlarge.png?m=1681798579", "created": 1666320525, "last_modified": 1681798579, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "hxzhouh1", "last_touched": 1783439964, "title": "这篇文章勾起了我的对于体罚的回忆", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1225465", "created": 1783388808, "deleted": 0, "content": "引用一下： https://www.v2ex.com/t/1225223#reply97\r\n\r\n时间：2005 年前后\r\n\r\n地点：广西武鸣双桥小学\r\n\r\n我在这个时间段转学到这所学校，语文老师是一个 30 左右的孕期女老师\r\n\r\n她多次直接拿书本/用手直接狂扇学生脸，没有任何人敢反抗，记忆有点模糊，说不上是因为什么，但是她好像是只针对某一个或某几个学生；回想起来，好像也从来没有学生家长来闹过，直到小升初结束，她还继续正常在教书\r\n\r\n这简直是我见过的最扯最让人心惊肉跳的老师，我要是这同学，估计都得 ptsd 了，也不知道他现在咋样了", "content_rendered": "<p>引用一下： <a href=\"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1225223#reply97\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.v2ex.com/t/1225223#reply97</a></p>\n<p>时间：2005 年前后</p>\n<p>地点：广西武鸣双桥小学</p>\n<p>我在这个时间段转学到这所学校，语文老师是一个 30 左右的孕期女老师</p>\n<p>她多次直接拿书本/用手直接狂扇学生脸，没有任何人敢反抗，记忆有点模糊，说不上是因为什么，但是她好像是只针对某一个或某几个学生；回想起来，好像也从来没有学生家长来闹过，直到小升初结束，她还继续正常在教书</p>\n<p>这简直是我见过的最扯最让人心惊肉跳的老师，我要是这同学，估计都得 ptsd 了，也不知道他现在咋样了</p>\n", "last_modified": 1783388808, "replies": 66, "id": 1225465}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_large.png?m=1768280127", "name": "career", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_normal.png?m=1768280127", "title": "职场话题", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/career", "topics": 23787, "footer": "", "header": "这里，我们聊聊那些工作中遇到的开心和不开心的事。", "title_alternative": "Career", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1768280127", "stars": 3706, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 770, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"id": 578299, "username": "nanofei", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/nanofei", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/033e/c2fb/578299_mini.png?m=1690007092", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/033e/c2fb/578299_normal.png?m=1690007092", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/033e/c2fb/578299_large.png?m=1690007092", "avatar_xlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/033e/c2fb/578299_xlarge.png?m=1690007092", "avatar_xxlarge": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/033e/c2fb/578299_xxlarge.png?m=1690007092", "created": 1649987466, "last_modified": 1690007092, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "OC0311", "last_touched": 1783443856, "title": "面了个虚拟货币相关的菲律宾公司，转正后去东京可以去吗", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1225533", "created": 1783397543, "deleted": 0, "content": "说是国内试用期 3 个月远程发 u ，\r\n试用期转正后要去东京，包住。交当地最低社保，其余的发 u ，3 个月有一周假期可以回国。\r\n具体内容好像是做虚拟货币游戏的，按我以前玩的经验。。应该是涉 db 的。\r\n相关法律风险搜了下，好像不在国内和日本本土运营就不违法\r\n\r\n能去吗。。谈薪给的有点高，是我之前的双倍。", "content_rendered": "说是国内试用期 3 个月远程发 u ，<br />试用期转正后要去东京，包住。交当地最低社保，其余的发 u ，3 个月有一周假期可以回国。<br />具体内容好像是做虚拟货币游戏的，按我以前玩的经验。。应该是涉 db 的。<br />相关法律风险搜了下，好像不在国内和日本本土运营就不违法<br /><br />能去吗。。谈薪给的有点高，是我之前的双倍。", "last_modified": 1783397583, "replies": 56, "id": 1225533}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1777132346", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1777132346", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 239761, "footer": "", "header": "<!--\r\n一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。\r\n-->", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1777132346", "stars": 4496, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 611298, "username": "owen800q", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/owen800q", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/757883d1d6cab2375e6331cbe648a7a9?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/757883d1d6cab2375e6331cbe648a7a9?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/757883d1d6cab2375e6331cbe648a7a9?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1674799402, "last_modified": 1781702576, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "dingawm", "last_touched": 1783474846, "title": "为什么中央政府不管控国人使用外国大模型？", "url": "htt